{"tid":878876,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"Supper Moment 同日本樂隊合作首新歌正到癲","createTime":"2018-10-27T13:14:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-01T18:23:30.000Z","uid":4203,"like":74,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"d0d5e12b57482292ba68b3370b53a045c6248283","tid":878876,"uid":4203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T13:14:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PHO7nTk7wsM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPHO7nTk7wsM&d=BBMsXovDUggW2io7Z2ScBVKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=6f25c067\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PHO7nTk7wsM</a><br />\n<br />\nSupper Moment x Survive Said The Prophet<br />\n<br />\n歌曲源於一個故事。<br />\n兩位識於微時的小伙子，從小到大都是同一所幼稚園、同所一小學、同一所中學；一起夾band，一起開始玩音樂。<br />\n中學後各散東西，一個去了日本、一個留在香港。各自組了自己的樂隊，也曾經遇到想放棄的時刻。<br />\n<br />\n今天，香港、日本兩個樂隊終於聚首，一起合作創作，<br />\n延續這首未完的詩。<br />\n<br />\n[To Whom]<br />\nWritten by Supper Moment &amp; Survive Said The Prophet<br />\nArranged by Supper Moment &amp; Survive Said The Prophet<br />\nProduced by Adrian Chan &amp; 王雙駿<br />\nMixed by Matthew Sim<br />\nMastered by Alex Psaroudakis at NYC<br />\nOP: Redline Music Limited / Sony Music Publishing (Japan) Inc.<br />\n<br />\nMV Directed by Hiroya Brian Nakano<br />\nSupper Moment:<br />\nHair by Nasaki Chu | Make up by Onki Lau <br />\nSurvive Said The Prophet:<br />\nHair and Make-up by Maila Tsuboi <br />\nWardrobes by Dr. Denim Japan"},{"pid":"cc4dbbd91ca1a045df93a07a9c2b616cef35fa5e","tid":878876,"uid":49941,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d0d5e12b57482292ba68b3370b53a045c6248283","tid":878876,"uid":4203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T13:14:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PHO7nTk7wsM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPHO7nTk7wsM&d=BBMsXovDUggW2io7Z2ScBVKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=6f25c067\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PHO7nTk7wsM</a><br />\n<br />\nSupper Moment x Survive Said The Prophet<br />\n<b